SONG CLUB
===

A tool for establishing community radio among a set of friends.

* Crawler - crawl, watch, and index local music
* Streaming - Allow individual and shared playback of music
* Liking - like, dislike, fave, and create playlists
* Activity - track new music and social activity
* RIYL - easily recommend music

License will most likely be under GPLv3


Requirements:

* Python 2.7
  * pyechonest
  * redis-py
  * tornado
  *

* Redis (2.4.14)

* Elastic Search

API
* Facebook
* Last.fm

For Installation Instructions, see the INSTALL doc.

For additional dev docs, see https://github.com/lhl/songclub/wiki
